Package com.kuryshee.schedulehelper

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GUI
    This class sets up the graphical interface.
    HTMLDownloader
    This class downloads data from SIS and parses it into @ScheduleBlock class instances.
    MyButton
    This class extends the @JButton with attributes for displaying the button as a schedule block in a table.
    MyButtonList
    This class is a specific container for the @MyButton class instances.
    ScheduleBlock
    This class is a structure for the time slot occupied by the lecture.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Day
    This enum structure helps to convert Czech day abbreviations to a reusable format.
    SubjectType
    This enum is for constants defining whether time slot contains lecture or practice.
